#: main_19.cpp:3
msgid "Start next time in normal screen"
msgstr "Fara lokaci na gaba a allon al'ada"

#: main_19.cpp:7
msgid "Start next time in full screen mode"
msgstr "Fara lokaci na gaba a yanayin cikakken allo"

#: main_19.cpp:9
msgid "If you exit the program from the menu, then the program"
msgstr "Idan ka fita daga shirin daga menu, to shirin"

#: main_19.cpp:11
msgid "will restart in normal 2d screen mode."
msgstr "zai sake farawa a yanayin allo na 2D na yau da kullun."

#: main_19.cpp:13
msgid "If you exit the program from the engine window toolbar,"
msgstr "Idan ka fita daga shirin daga kayan aikin taga injin,"

#: main_19.cpp:15
msgid "then the program will restart in full screen mode."
msgstr "to shirin zai sake farawa a yanayin cikakken allo."

#: main_19.cpp:17
msgid "Alternative - click to take back the reply move and play an alternative move instead."
msgstr "Madadin - danna don ɗaukar motsin amsawa kuma kunna madadin motsi maimakon."

#: main_19.cpp:19
msgid "To over-ride the default behaviour of this option"
msgstr "Don wuce gona da iri na ɗabi'ar wannan zaɓin"

#: main_19.cpp:21
msgid "Hold down < Ctrl > for the next alternative move in the list"
msgstr "Riƙe < Ctrl> don madadin da ke gaba a cikin jerin"

#: main_19.cpp:23
msgid "Hold down < Shift > for a random alternative move"
msgstr "Riƙe < Shift> don wani canji na daban da bazuwar"

#: main_19.cpp:25
msgid "Hold down < Ctrl > and < Shift > for the best alternative move"
msgstr "Riƙe < Ctrl> da < Shift> don mafi kyawun madadin motsi"

#: main_19.cpp:27
msgid "on the keyboard, select < File > < Exit 3d > from the main menu,"
msgstr "akan madannai, zaɓi < Fayil > < Fita 3d > daga babban menu,"

#: main_19.cpp:29
msgid "To exit the program from the 3d screen, select < File > < Exit program >"
msgstr "Don fita daga shirin daga allon 3d, zaɓi < Fayil > < Fita shirin >"

#: main_19.cpp:31
msgid "If the want to the program to restart in 3d graphics mode next time,"
msgstr "Idan kana son sake kunna shirin a yanayin zane-zane na 3D a lokaci na gaba,"

#: main_19.cpp:33
msgid "then hold down the < Ctrl > key when you select this option."
msgstr "sannan ka riƙe maɓallin < Ctrl> lokacin da ka zaɓi wannan zaɓin."

#: main_19.cpp:35
msgid "Adjourned games  -  Click to load a previously adjourned game."
msgstr "Wasannin da aka dakatar - Danna don loda wasan da aka dage a baya."

#: main_19.cpp:37
msgid "Load an adjourned game"
msgstr "Loda wasan da aka dakatar"

#: main_19.cpp:39
msgid "Adjourn game"
msgstr "Wasan da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:41
msgid "Open the Adjourned game dialog box"
msgstr "Buɗe akwatin tattaunawa na wasan da aka dakatar"

#: main_19.cpp:43
msgid "Adjourned games"
msgstr "Wasannin da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:45
msgid "Adjourned game file name"
msgstr "Sunan fayil ɗin wasan da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:47
msgid "Select adjourned game .pgn filename"
msgstr "Zaɓi sunan fayil ɗin wasan .pgn da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:49
msgid "Load"
msgstr "Loda"

#: main_19.cpp:51
msgid "Enter the PGN adjourn game file name"
msgstr "Shigar da sunan fayil ɗin wasan dakatarwar PGN"

#: main_19.cpp:52
msgid "Save the current game as adjouned"
msgstr "Ajiye wasan da ake yi a yanzu kamar an sake shi"

#: main_19.cpp:53
msgid "Load the adjourned game as current"
msgstr "Loda wasan da aka dage kamar yadda yake a yanzu"

#: main_19.cpp:55
msgid "This dialog box allows you to adjourn a game and restart it later."
msgstr "Wannan akwatin tattaunawa yana ba ku damar dage wasa kuma ku sake kunna shi daga baya."

#: main_19.cpp:57
msgid "Click the < Save > button to save the current game."
msgstr "Danna maɓallin < Ajiye > don adana wasan da ake yi yanzu."

#: main_19.cpp:59
msgid "You can them choose the PGN file for saving the game in"
msgstr "Za ka iya zaɓar fayil ɗin PGN don adana wasan a ciki"

#: main_19.cpp:61
msgid "and then you can enter the game details."
msgstr "sannan za ku iya shigar da cikakkun bayanai game da wasan."

#: main_19.cpp:63
msgid "Click the < Load > button to load a previously stored game."
msgstr "Danna maɓallin <Load> don loda wasan da aka adana a baya."

#: main_19.cpp:65
msgid "As before you choose the PGN file to load the game from,"
msgstr "Kamar yadda a da ka zaɓi fayil ɗin PGN don loda wasan daga ciki,"

#: main_19.cpp:67
msgid "and then you can pick the game that you want."
msgstr "sannan zaka iya zaɓar wasan da kake so."

#: main_19.cpp:69
msgid "If you click < Ok > the game will be loaded, ready for playing."
msgstr "Idan ka danna < Ok> za a loda wasan, a shirye don yin wasa."

#: main_19.cpp:71
msgid "Then pick < Play white > or < Play black > depending on which colour"
msgstr "Sannan zaɓi < Kunna fari> ko < Kunna baƙi> ya danganta da launin da kuke so"

#: main_19.cpp:73
msgid "you had in the adjourned game."
msgstr "kun yi a wasan da aka dage."

#: main_19.cpp:75
msgid "Adjourned games can also be restarted from the rated game dialog box."
msgstr "Ana iya sake kunna wasannin da aka dage daga akwatin tattaunawar wasan da aka kimanta."

#: main_19.cpp:77
msgid "If you load a game from there, it will be automatically ready for play,"
msgstr "Idan ka loda wasa daga nan, zai kasance a shirye ta atomatik don wasa,"

#: main_19.cpp:79
msgid "although your clock will not start until you make a move."
msgstr "kodayake agogonka ba zai fara ba har sai ka yi motsi."

#: main_19.cpp:81
msgid "Adjourn game dialog box"
msgstr "Akwatin tattaunawa na wasan da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:83
msgid "Error writing clock config file"
msgstr "Kuskure wajen rubuta fayil ɗin saita agogo"

#: main_19.cpp:85
msgid "Invalid PGN file name"
msgstr "Sunan fayil ɗin PGN mara inganci"

#: main_19.cpp:87
msgid "Cannot open clock config file"
msgstr "Ba za a iya buɗe fayil ɗin saita agogo ba"

#: main_19.cpp:89
msgid "Adjourned game saved"
msgstr "An adana wasan da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:91
msgid "Adjourned game loaded"
msgstr "An ɗora wasan da aka dage"

#: main_19.cpp:93
msgid "Error reading clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "Kuskuren karanta fayil ɗin saita agogo, an soke aikin"

#: main_19.cpp:95
msgid "Could not open clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "Ba za a iya buɗe fayil ɗin saita agogo ba, an soke aikin"

#: main_19.cpp:97
msgid "Could not find clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "An kasa samun fayil ɗin saita agogo, an soke aikin"

#: main_19.cpp:99
msgid "Press < Ok > to transfer the game to the board"
msgstr "Danna < Ok > don canja wurin wasan zuwa allon"

#: main_19.cpp:101
msgid "Adjourned game options"
msgstr "Zaɓuɓɓukan wasan da aka dage"
